   Ushimaru, Atushi; Seo, Natsumi, Kobe Univ, Grad Sch Human Dev \& Environm, Kobe, Japan.
   Ushimaru, Atushi; Seo, Natsumi, Kobe Univ, Fac Human Dev, Kobe, Japan.
   Sakagami, Kota; Funamoto, Daichi, Kobe Univ, Grad Sch Agr Sci, Kobe, Japan.
   Funamoto, Daichi, Univ Tokyo, Grad Sch Sci, Bot Gardens, Tokyo, Japan.
   Funamoto, Daichi, Tokyo Univ Agr, Fac Agr, Tokyo, Japan.
   Ushimaru, Atushi, Nada, 3-11 Tsurukabuto, Kobe 6578501, Japan.},
